  "text": "Five to six 310 6 Gr-1 + cells, obtained from a pool of two animals, were crosslinked for 5 min at room temperature and ChIP assays performed as previously described [CITATION_1] . Antibodies used were acetylated H3 Lys 27 (H3K27Ac) (ab4729; Abcam) and IgG. Primer sequences and full protocol details are given in Supplementary Experimental Procedures.",
